Top-Seeded Yale Defeats Air Force in Overtime at NCAA Hockey Tournament

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-03-26T01:26:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-26/top-seeded-yale-defeats-air-force-in-overtime-at-ncaa-hockey-tournament.html
Top-seeded  Yale University  defeated
the U.S.  Air Force  Academy 2-1 on an overtime goal by Chad
Ziegler to advance to the second round of the national college
tournament.  Yale next will face Minnesota-Duluth tomorrow at the
Webster Bank Arena in Bridgeport,  Connecticut , in the National
Collegiate Athletic Association tournament. Minnesota-Duluth
(23-10-6) defeated Union College 2-0 today in the first round.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  